se.axisandandroids.buffer
Class FrameBuffer

java.lang.Object
  se.axisandandroids.buffer.FrameBuffer

public class FrameBuffer
extends java.lang.Object

A circular buffer providing mailbox for Frame objects. Designed to avoid repeated object creation, ie. the Frame objects in the fixed size buffer is reused when put(byte[] x, int len) and get(byte[] jpeg) which instead just copy byte arrays.

Author:
jg
